Class PropertyAccessorDelegate<A extends Properties<A>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.co.strangeskies.utilities.ObservableImpl<A>

  • Type Parameters:

    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Properties<A>, Copyable<A>, Observable<A>, Self<A>

    public class PropertyAccessorDelegate<A extends Properties<A>>
extends ObservableImpl<A>
implements Properties<A>
    Delegate implementation object for proxy instances of property accessor interfaces. This class deals with most method interception from the proxies generated by PropertyLoader.
